comments: Huerter (SAC) is moving alongside Garland's (CLE) path and marginal body contact occurs during Garland's (CLE) drive.
Sabonis (SAC) avoids making arm contact and cleanly blocks Garland's (CLE) driving shot attempt.
Garland (CLE) moves laterally into Barnes' (SAC) path and initiates body contact that affects Barnes' (SAC) SQBR during the drive.
Mobley (CLE) establishes himself in Mitchell's (SAC) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Allen (CLE) establishes himself in Mitchell's (SAC) path and his legs remain within the frame of his body as contact occurs, which he does not deliver.
Sabonis (SAC) initiates contact with Garland's (CLE) head during the drive.
Barnes (SAC) establishes himself in Garland's (CLE) path and his legs remain within the frame of his body as marginal contact occurs, and Garland is able to move though the pick.
Barnes (SAC) establishes himself in Garland's (CLE) path and marginal contact occurs as he sets the pick.
Murray (SAC) briefly brings his hands forward and marginal contact occurs during Garland's (CLE) drive.
Osman (CLE) extends both hands forward and initiates contact with Mitchell (SAC), which affects Mitchell's (SAC) SQBR.
Allen (CLE) gives a step of distance when establishing himself in Murray's (SAC) path and marginal contact occurs during the pick.
LeVert (CLE) wraps Barnes (SAC) and affects his FOM.
Garland (CLE) dribbles the clock out and the shot clock expires.
